"1/4 cup roughly chopped fresh rosemary","2 tablespoons fresh thyme","2 tablespoons roughly chopped fresh parsley","6  large cloves garlic, roughly chopped","2 teaspoons grated lemon zest (from 2 lemons)","3  tinned anchovy fillets","1 teaspoon pepper","1/4 cup olive oil","1  semi-boneless leg of lamb, trimmed and tied (7 to 8 lb.)"